{"word":"ἀποξενόω","slug":"ἀποξενόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποξενόω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀπόξενος'><el>ἀπόξενος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to drive from house and home, banish</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>γῆς ἀποξενοῦσθαι</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}